@prefix sh:      <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#> .
@prefix rdf:     <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs:    <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix xsd:     <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix obo:     <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/> .
@prefix time:    <http://www.w3.org/2006/time#> .
@prefix ti-o:    <https://w3id.org/zinl/ti-o#> .
@prefix :        <https://w3id.org/zinl/ti-o/shacl#> .

# # ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# # Identifier pattern used throughout:
# #
# #   entity  <-- obo:IAO_0000219 (denotes) --  CRID (IAO_0000578)
# #   CRID    --> obo:BFO_0000050 (part_of) -->  ti-o:CodeSystem
# #   CRID    --> obo:IAO_0000577            -->  xsd:string
# #
# # In SHACL we navigate via the inverse of denotes (IAO_0000235 / denoted by):
# #   entity  --> obo:IAO_0000235 (denoted by) --> CRID
# # ---------------------------------------------------------------------------


